title: How to help your customers choose

displayTitle:
“Right, so you have a super king bed? Let me show you the programs we offer that come in that size.”

***

“What feeling do you like against your skin when you get into bed? These Vue Superfine sheets are lovely and crisp, or if you prefer a silky and smooth sensation, there are several sateen sheets I could show you?”

***

“I hear you when you say you haven’t got time to spend fussing over care instructions for your sheets, and we’ve got the perfect Easy Care sheets for you. An added bonus is that they’re super affordable, too.”

***

“So you’re looking for something in navy to complement your bedroom’s new colour scheme? Both Heritage and Australian House & Garden have programs that offer what you’re after. Let me get those sheets for you.”
